1052
01:14:11,999 --> 01:14:14,672
but I appreciate him
sending us your novel.

1053
01:14:15,319 --> 01:14:16,547
Did you like it?

1054
01:14:16,839 --> 01:14:20,354
It has its ups and downs,
but it's fits the market now.

1055
01:14:21,359 --> 01:14:24,192
