1070
01:15:30,559 --> 01:15:31,628
I was going to yawn.

1071
01:15:31,799 --> 01:15:34,438
Don't be cruel.
What do you want me to say?

1072
01:15:34,599 --> 01:15:36,032
Men make mistakes.

1073
01:15:36,199 --> 01:15:37,314
If you say so.

1074
01:15:38,319 --> 01:15:39,638
Diego was right.

1075
01:15:40,519 --> 01:15:43,317
- Deep down, you're all the same.
