for their actions.

1095
01:16:59,199 --> 01:17:00,518
And for what they are.

1096
01:17:01,279 --> 01:17:02,598
I want to marry you.

1097
01:17:02,839 --> 01:17:05,069
- Are you feeling all right?
- I was sick...

1098
01:17:05,639 --> 01:17:10,030
but it's the best thing that
could have happened.

1099
01:17:10,639 --> 01:17:12,118
Now I see everything clearly.

1100
01:17:12,319 --> 01:17:13,593
I need you more than ever.

1101
01:17:13,759 --> 01:17:14,748
Of course.

1102
01:17:15,399 --> 01:17:17,549
- The possessive thing.
- No,

1103
01:17:17,719 --> 01:17:19,152
I don't want to own you.

1104
01:17:19,679 --> 01:17:22,318
I want to be yours
and nobody else's.

1105
01:17:22,919 --> 01:17:23,669
Do you understand?

1106
01:17:24,959 --> 01:17:26,358
I love you, Silvia.

1107
01:17:27,039 --> 01:17:28,472
I swear I love you.

1108
01:17:50,679 --> 01:17:51,634
Silvia,

1109
01:17:52,759 --> 01:17:53,748
was it that night?

1110
01:17:55,119 --> 01:17:55,869
